Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:50.36,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(720,658)}ゆら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「暮色」「川急」
