Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「神代有蓬莱」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牌的数目并不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「相信我吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是书桌小子帮我发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉了我「你能听到」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:11:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「我很羡慕」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:01.28,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,うかりける
