Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.69,0:22:19.85,ed25_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fad(300,300)}因为你会说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:24.09,ed25_cn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fad(300,300)}「我肯定也和你一样」
